---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon'
import "../styles/global.css";
import Navigation from "../components/Navigation.astro"; "../components/Navigation.astro";
const title = "Welcome!";
import memoji from "../assets/devMemoji2.png"
import Slider from "../components/slider.astro"
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{title}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
          <Navigation />
          <div id="Home" class="w-full h-screen text-center">
               <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl p-2 w-full h-full flex justify-center items-center">
                    <div>
                         <h2 class="text-tan text-6xl py-2 font-semibold font-Chillax">Hello World, I'm <span class="text-red-950
                         hover:text-7xl ease-in duration-300 font-[poppins]">Chinedum Nmereole</span>,</h2>
                         <h3 class="text-tan text-4xl py-2 font-semibold font-Chillax">A Software Engineer and Fullstack Developer</h3>
                         <p class="text-md max-w-[70%] m-auto leading-7 text-zinc-600 text-xl">I am a recent graduate in
                         with a Bachelors of Science in Software Engineering, I am excited to showcase my skills and passion for creating innovative solutions. With a strong foundation in programming and a commitment to continuous learning, I am eager to contribute to a dynamic software engineering role. Thank you for visiting, and let's connect to explore potential opportunities.</p>
                         <div class="m-2 p-2 flex content-center justify-center gap-12">
                         <Icon name="mdi:github" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full text-tan cursor-pointer hover:scale-150 hover:text-red-950" />
                         <Icon name="mdi:linkedin" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full text-tan cursor-pointer hover:scale-150 hover:text-red-950"/>
                         <Icon name="mdi:at" class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full text-tan cursor-pointer hover:scale-150 hover:text-red-950"/>
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>
        
          <div id="About" class="w-full md:h-screen items-center flex p-2 py-16">
               <div class="max-w-[1280px] m-auto md:grid grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="col-span-2">
                         <p class="tracking-wider flex justify-left items-left uppercase text-blackboard text-2xl font-bold hover:scale-110 ease-in
                         duration-300 font-Chillax">About</p>
                         <h2 class="items-left flex justify-left text-tan text-4xl py-2 font-Stardom">Get to know Me</h2>
                         <p class="items-left flex text-left justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2 font-[poppins]">Hello! I'm
                         Chinedum Nmereole, a passionate software engineer based in Huntsville, Texas. I recently
                         graduated from Sam Houston State University with a degree in Software Engineering. Originally
                         hailing from Spartanburg, South Carolina, I made the exciting decision to pursue my education
                         in Texas, and it has been an incredible journey so far.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2 font-[poppins]">My love for problem-solving and creating innovative solutions led me to the field of software engineering. I thrive in the dynamic and ever-evolving world of technology, where I can apply my knowledge and skills to develop robust and efficient software applications.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2 font-[poppins]">Beyond coding, I have diverse interests that keep me engaged outside the realm of programming. I find inspiration and excitement in combat sports such as boxing and MMA. The discipline, strategy, and physicality of these sports constantly push me to challenge myself and strive for personal growth.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2
                         font-[poppins]">In addition to combat sports, I have a deep appreciation for the strategic game
                         of chess. The mental agility and focus required in each move captivate me, and I enjoy
                         exploring different strategies and tactics.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2
                         font-[poppins]">Through my portfolio website, I aim to showcase my skills and projects as a software engineer while also sharing a glimpse of my interests and personality. I believe in continuous learning and staying updated with the latest technologies and industry trends.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2
                         font-[poppins]">If you're looking for a dedicated and versatile software engineer or if you simply want to connect and discuss common interests, I would love to hear from you. Let's collaborate and make a positive impact together.</p>
                         <p class="items-left text-left flex justify-left text-blackboard text-md py-2
                         font-[poppins]">Thank you for visiting my portfolio website, and I look forward to connecting with you!</p>

                    </div>
                    <div class="relative mx-auto h-auto w-full flex justify-center content-center overflow-hidden
                    shadow-xl shadow-darkgrain rounded-xl hover:scale-110 ease-in duration-300 bg-tan">
                         <img src={memoji} alt="memoji of chinedum nmereole" class="object-cover">
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>
          <div id="Skills" class="w-full lg:h-screen items-center flex p-2 py-16">
               <div class="max-w-[1240px] m-auto md:grid grid-cols-5 grid-rows-2 gap-8">
                    <div class="col-span-5">
                         <h2 class=" flex justify-left items-left font-bold uppercase text-blackboard text-2xl
                         font-Chillax hover:scale-110 ease-in
                         duration-300">Skills</h2>
                         <h2 class="items-left flex justify-left text-tan text-4xl py-2 font-Stardom">Things I can do</h2>
                         <Slider />
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>
	</body>
    
</html>
